{"title":"BloqueoAV Completo iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/BloqueoAV Completo iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Bloqueo AV Completo\\N(3er Grado)","guid":"072Ut_kKrFb4ihwLeuBhYw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definicion","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Disociacion COMPLETA auricula-ventriculo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Ninguna onda P se conduce al ventriculo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Ritmo auricular y ventricular INDEPENDIENTES","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Frecuencia auricular > frecuencia ventricular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Requiere ritmo de escape para mantener gasto cardiaco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Anatomia del sistema\\Nde conduccion","guid":"XAqQyJbczW947Tmvbg0Z2g","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Nodo AV → localizado\\Nen triangulo de Koch","guid":"GOn0Mi2jL8Vc__QxOYPSPA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Limite posterior: tendon de Todaro","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"Limite inferior: valva tricuspidea (anillo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Limite anterior: seno coronario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Haz de His → atraviesa cuerpo fibroso central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"Ramas izquierda y derecha","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"7","text":"Irrigacion nodo AV →\\Narteria del nodo AV","guid":"0ADZrFoNgQKrIazBZZRNNw","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"90% rama de coronaria derecha","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"10% rama de circunfleja","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiologia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Incidencia aumenta con edad → envejecimiento del sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Causa mas frecuente en AM: degeneracion fibrotica (enfermedad de Lev-Lenegre)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Prevalencia ~0.04% poblacion general","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"Post-TAVI: 10-25% requieren marcapasos permanente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"17","text":"Post-cirugia cardiaca: 1-4%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Etiologia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"DEGENERATIVA\\N(MAS FRECUENTE\\Nen AM)","guid":"sLo9tmXJWf2Td061_bpadg","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Enfermedad de Lev → fibrosis esqueleto cardiaco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Enfermedad de Lenegre → degeneracion primaria del sistema His-Purkinje","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Calcificacion anillo mitral/aortico → extension al sistema de conduccion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"Isquemica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"IAM inferior → bloqueo\\Nnodal, generalmente\\NTRANSITORIO","guid":"VnuamwFTk6usybW1J5CHiA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Ritmo de escape estrecho (~40-60 lpm)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"Responde a atropina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Resolucion espontanea en 5-7 dias (mayoria)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"IAM anterior → bloqueo infranodal,\\NMAL PRONOSTICO","guid":"BG9j0rI8WTNnbSkurr8eKg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Ritmo de escape ancho (<40 lpm)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"NO responde a atropina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Indica necrosis extensa del septum","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"23","text":"Farmacologica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Betabloqueadores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Calcioantagonistas no-DHP (verapamilo, diltiazem)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Digoxina → intoxicacion digitalica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"Amiodarona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"Ivabradina (inhibidor HCN4) → puede prolongar PR/AH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"EVALUAR SIEMPRE deprescripcion antes de marcapasos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"23","text":"Infecciosa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Endocarditis → absceso anillo aortico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Enfermedad de Lyme → borreliosis, reversible con ATB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Chagas → endemia latinoamericana, fibrosis miocardica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Miocarditis viral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"23","text":"Infiltrativa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Amiloidosis cardiaca (AL y ATTR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Sarcoidosis → indicacion de RM cardiaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Hemocromatosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"23","text":"Autoinmune","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Lupus neonatal → anti-Ro/SSA, anti-La/SSB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Miastenia gravis → bloqueo AV reportado (raro)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"23","text":"Congenita","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Aislada → mutacion NKX2-5, TBX5, SCN5A","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Asociada a cardiopatias congenitas\\N(TGA corregida, CIA tipo ostium primum)","guid":"lEVqYUwAbtX44Rjk9y7ZsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"23","text":"Iatrogenica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Post-TAVI → persiste >24-48h = indicacion MCP (ESC 2021 Clase I)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Post-cirugia cardiaca → si persiste >5 dias = indicacion MCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Ablacion por radiofrecuencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatologia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Nivel del bloqueo →\\Ndetermina pronostico","guid":"9GPFp3vWNTJZpMWmG9ESzg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"SUPRAHISIANO\\N(nodal)","guid":"jRRkYUXqdlj90I0VyhesgA","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Ritmo de escape ESTRECHO (QRS <120ms)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"FC escape 40-60 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Relativamente estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Puede responder a atropina/isoproterenol","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"INFRAHISIANO\\N(His-Purkinje)","guid":"rA6wHldbjZMHrmvd25fbZg","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Ritmo de escape ANCHO (QRS >120ms)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"FC escape 20-40 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"INESTABLE → alto riesgo de asistolia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"NO responde a atropina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"PEOR PRONOSTICO → indicacion URGENTE de MCP","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"63","text":"Dependencia del\\Nritmo de escape","guid":"Nf8oSk_aDzVzyheVsQ9bhg","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Escape nodal → mas rapido y confiable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"Escape ventricular → lento, irregular, riesgo de TV/FV","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"63","text":"Disminucion gasto cardiaco → sincope (Stokes-Adams)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"63","text":"Remodelamiento cardiaco → dilatacion ventricular si cronico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"0","text":"Clinica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Sintomas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Sincope/presincope (ataques de Stokes-Adams) → CLASICO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Disnea de esfuerzo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"Fatiga, astenia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"Mareo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"82","text":"Insuficiencia cardiaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"82","text":"Muerte subita (si escape inadecuado)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"81","text":"ASINTOMATICO → posible en bloqueo AV congenito","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Aun asi: indicacion de MCP si factores de riesgo (ESC 2021)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"81","text":"Signos al\\Nexamen\\Nfisico","guid":"yalqxvqN-n4IUDtpSzyPTA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Bradicardia (generalmente <50 lpm)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Ondas A en canon → contraccion auricular contra valvula cerrada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"Variacion intensidad R1 → disociacion AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"PA sistolica elevada (aumento volumen sistolico compensatorio)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"Diagnostico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"ECG 12 derivaciones\\N→ GOLD STANDARD","guid":"zy36YW9SCNnSWh4wApUEpg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Ondas P regulares a su frecuencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Complejos QRS regulares a su frecuencia (MENOR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"NO relacion entre P y QRS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"Intervalo PP constante, intervalo RR constante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"Distincion clave: QRS estrecho vs ancho → nivel del bloqueo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"Holter 24-48h → bloqueo intermitente/paroxistico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"96","text":"Estudio electrofisiologico\\N(EEF)","guid":"olzXpKE0c5kb-QcW-aZYlw","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Indicado si sitio de bloqueo incierto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"Intervalo AH prolongado → bloqueo nodal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"Intervalo HV prolongado o ausente → bloqueo infranodal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"96","text":"Laboratorio\\Ncomplementario","guid":"srkX3sCT990-4-shTlLlGA","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Electrolitos (K+, Ca2+, Mg2+)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Funcion tiroidea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Digoxinemia si sospecha intoxicacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"Serologia Lyme (areas endemicas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"Anti-Ro/Anti-La (si lupus neonatal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"108","text":"Troponinas (si sospecha isquemica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"96","text":"Imagen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Ecocardiograma → funcion VI, cardiopatia estructural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"RM cardiaca → sarcoidosis, miocarditis, amiloidosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"TC coronario → si sospecha isquemica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"Manejo\\Nagudo","guid":"3AdG0JCuc9-j1bzagL0yaw","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"ESTABLE\\Nhemodinamicamente","guid":"yYhlIRXsnxmRR-F_lPMhrw","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Monitoreo continuo ECG","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Evaluar y SUSPENDER farmacos bradicardizantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"Preparar marcapasos transcutaneo (parches)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"INESTABLE →\\NALGORITMO\\NBRADICARDIA ACLS","guid":"NaoQE-VuDJyOy7uCtrvkdw","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Atropina 0.5mg IV\\N(puede repetir hasta\\N3mg)","guid":"sbDQA-4P7C9qtKvMC9oaSg","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"UTIL en bloqueo suprahisiano","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"INUTIL/PERJUDICIAL en infrahisiano","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"Marcapasos transcutaneo →\\NPRIMERA LINEA si inestable","guid":"5bgnkcr2HqbSMqxKJQm1bA","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"FC programada 60-80 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Incrementar mA hasta captura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Verificar captura mecanica (pulso)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"Sedacion/analgesia si consciente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"124","text":"Infusion cronotropica\\N(puente a MCP transitorio)","guid":"JLX27yJHPBUzgsOB16pw8g","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Isoproterenol 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Dopamina 5-20 mcg/kg/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Epinefrina 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"124","text":"Marcapasos transvenoso\\NTEMPORAL","guid":"wjp0LhsVdE1P_s5eSofHHg","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"Via venosa central (yugular/subclavia/femoral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"Punta en apex VD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"Verificar umbral de captura y sensado","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Manejo definitivo →\\NMARCAPASOS PERMANENTE","guid":"i0hEWhyS4aIYUifT_m9WWA","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Indicaciones\\NESC 2021","guid":"h2qx3u6tHyiO3dZQnZwegg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"CLASE I\\N(recomendado)","guid":"svU3sU3tepbJaQNJb254wQ","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"BAV completo sintomatico → independiente del nivel","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"BAV completo\\Nasintomatico con\\Ncualquiera de","guid":"ySFNglMPPk-w7bd4k0zqzg","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"FC diurna promedio <50 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Pausas >3x ciclo del ritmo de escape","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"QRS escape ancho","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"145","text":"QT prolongado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"145","text":"Ectopia ventricular compleja","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"143","text":"BAV completo post-TAVI persistente >24-48h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"143","text":"BAV completo post-IAM que no resuelve en <5 dias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"142","text":"CLASE I → incluso ASINTOMATICO tiene indicacion pronostica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"141","text":"Seleccion del\\Ndispositivo","guid":"PgA5dw5Lh51oT8sO__LrUA","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Bicameral (DDD) →\\NPREFERIDO en ritmo sinusal","guid":"DOmOL4QUmsA4S5xsj-3I6A","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Preserva sincronia AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Permite tracking auricular","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"Monocameral (VVI) → FA permanente con BAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"154","text":"CRT (TRC) → si FEVI <40% y alta\\Ncarga de estimulacion VD esperada","guid":"ot3IkHZ5OHDG3gpWjpwP4g","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"ESC 2021 Clase I: FEVI <40% + necesidad pacing → CRT sobre VD pacing","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Prevenir miocardiopatia inducida por estimulacion VD","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"154","text":"Estimulacion del\\Nsistema de conduccion\\N(CSP)","guid":"xHHyu_BvghWjF-SErMFfUQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"His Bundle Pacing (HBP) → fisiologico pero challenging","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Left Bundle Branch Pacing (LBBP) → emergente, mas estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"ALTERNATIVA a CRT si implante seno coronario fallido (Clase IIa)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"154","text":"Marcapasos sin cables\\N(leadless)","guid":"Xf6wQreffGyGZ56-ah0Vdw","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Considerar si acceso venoso dificil o alto riesgo infeccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"Solo estimulacion VVI por ahora","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"141","text":"Seguimiento\\Npost-implante","guid":"K_KieHNrTzo_FcbghbYw9w","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Control a 1-3 meses, luego cada 6-12 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"Monitoreo remoto → recomendado (ESC 2021)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"Evaluar dependencia de marcapasos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"Vigilar miocardiopatia inducida por pacing → ecocardiograma","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones geriatricas\\NESPECIFICAS","guid":"5wbFPdbeOEs443dnsq1jXw","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"Degeneracion sistema conduccion → causa mas frecuente en >75 anos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"Comorbilidad y fragilidad →\\Nevaluar CFS antes de MCP","guid":"JvY4hjYdwOH_TkyGvdfCbQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"CFS >=7 → discusion proporcionalidad terapeutica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Beneficio vs riesgo procedimiento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"174","text":"Polifarmacia → revisar SIEMPRE\\Nfarmacos bradicardizantes","guid":"_i89SZRd0U_AqUoe05Wo_Q","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"DEPRESCRIBIR antes de indicar MCP si posible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"STOPP criteria: betabloqueadores en bradicardia <50 lpm","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"174","text":"Sincope en AM → BAV completo en diagnostico diferencial SIEMPRE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"174","text":"Riesgo caidas → BAV paroxistico subdiagnosticado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"174","text":"Delirium post-implante → prevencion multicomponente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"174","text":"Miocardiopatia inducida\\Npor estimulacion VD","guid":"Gio0ij74QL-CZsn6SQ2saQ","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"AM mas susceptibles por reserva miocardica reducida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Considerar CRT/CSP de inicio si FEVI borderline","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"174","text":"DECISION COMPARTIDA →\\Ninformar pronostico con/sin MCP","guid":"FMy8oGWgSpNqDFusqaR49A","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"En BAV completo, MCP mejora SUPERVIVENCIA (no solo sintomas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Discutir con paciente y familia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"174","text":"RM cardiaca → MRI-conditional devices disponibles","guid":"","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Sarcoidosis/amiloidosis como causa en AM → estudio mandatorio","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"BAV completo ASINTOMATICO igual requiere MCP → beneficio pronostico (ESC 2021 Clase I)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"QRS escape ANCHO = infrahisiano = URGENCIA → no esperar sintomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"En AM: SIEMPRE descartar farmacos como causa ANTES de MCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"193","text":"Post-IAM inferior: BAV generalmente transitorio → esperar 5 dias antes de MCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"193","text":"Post-IAM anterior: BAV = necrosis extensa → mal pronostico independiente del MCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"193","text":"FEVI <40% + indicacion de pacing → CRT sobre estimulacion VD convencional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"193","text":"Ivabradina puede causar/empeorar bloqueo AV → revisar si paciente la usa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"193","text":"Ondas A en canon al examen fisico → signo clasico de disociacion AV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"193","text":"En Chagas endemico (Latinoamerica): BAV completo en adulto joven → pensar siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"193","text":"Marcapasos leadless: opcion en AM con acceso venoso dificil o infecciones previas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"→ Bradicardia y marcapasos (Cardiologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"→ Farmacologia cardiovascular (Farmacologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"→ Sincope (Cardiologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"→ Envejecimiento cardiovascular (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"204","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"204","text":"→ Deprescripcion (Farmacologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"204","text":"→ Fragilidad (Valoracion Geriatrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"204","text":"→ Proporcionalidad terapeutica (Bioetica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"1. Glikson M, et al. 2021 ESC Guidelines on cardiac pacing and cardiac resynchronization therapy. Eur Heart J. 2021;42(35):3427-3520.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"2. Kusumoto FM, et al. 2018 ACC/AHA/HRS Guideline on the Evaluation and Management of Patients With Bradycardia. J Am Coll Cardiol. 2019;74(7):e51-e156.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"3. Khalid A, et al. Comparative effects of biventricular and right ventricular pacing on clinical outcomes in AV block: systematic review and meta-analysis. BMC Cardiovasc Disord. 2025;25(1):835.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"213","text":"4. Dogan M, Canpolat U. Alternatives to right ventricular pacing in patients with AV block. Expert Rev Cardiovasc Ther. 2026;24(2):107-113.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"213","text":"5. Copier JS, et al. HCN4 in the atrioventricular node. Heart Rhythm. 2025;22(9):2160-2173.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"213","text":"6. Brignole M, et al. 2018 ESC Guidelines for the diagnosis and management of syncope. Eur Heart J. 2018;39(21):1883-1948.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"213","text":"7. Michowitz Y, et al. The 10 commandments for the 2021 ESC guidelines on cardiac pacing and CRT. Eur Heart J. 2021;42(44):4295.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":220,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"BloqueoAV Completo iPad","id":"map_232","resolved_references":[]}